1. Videla sam *zvono* na vratima. (I saw a *bell* on the door.)
2. Na zvonu pise "Ne uznemiravajte psa". (The *bell* says "Do not disturb the dog".)
3. Nisam culjla *zvona* sa svojih rukava. (I haven't heard any *bells* from my sleeves.)
4. Prekinuli smo veceru kad je *zvono* zazvonilo. (We interrupted dinner when the *bell* rang.)
5. Ona je *zvonar* u crkvi. (She is a *bell ringer* in the church.)
6. *Zvonic* je pozvao tri puta ali niko nije odgovorio. (The *bellboy* called three times but nobody answered.)
7. On je *zvonar* odlican u svom poslu. (He is an excellent *bell ringer* in his job.)
8. *Zvonjava* je bila toliko glasna da sam se probudila. (The *ringing* was so loud that I woke up.)
9. Kupili smo *zvono* da objesimo na na≈°u kucu. (We bought a *bell* to hang on our house.)
10. Nije mi se svideo *zvuk* tog zvona. (I didn't like the *sound* of that bell.)